                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18420131-839-offence-1 t18420131-cd-224"></join>12th of January</rs>, a forged request for the delivery of goods, with intent to defraud <persName id="t18420131-name-1317" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-1317" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420131-name-1317" type="surname" value="MOSER"></interp>
